    {
      "chinese": "部落在民國58年發生火災，不幸罹難的村民有47人，房屋燒毀148戶，重創我們家園。我們度過一段缺糧、沒水、沒電的難民日子。族人經過數十年努力災後重建，才慢慢地恢復「Taromak」新的家園。",
      "ab": "cekelenai Taromak sa malimalre si valro ka cayli kwalraobo, la wa’acay ka ta maso’atelre si ’ito ka omase, kwalraobo ka iday si maso’atelre si valro ka daane, takolraoba amatikoro naiya sa madraw ’aramoro, kadrowa ka acilray si dinki, lramani sa marathodo makeceng nai ka sakaocekelra, tara mangealre silabalre takikwaliya, la modrare’e kai soTaromak.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2025/03/05/97b4dca1a1e2470744c8e6d6be47230c.wav",
